{"h532333abg63feg43bcg9190g4391c3356549": ["Better not touch the webs. I'd hate to disturb the locals.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "8b8f9633-6b35-7cf5-15a6-e1cc5aac505e"], "h95a1104dg4af0g44aag9982g5a7eb73cf97b": ["Better not disturb these webs. Whatever wove them would be much too large for my liking.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "8b8f9633-6b35-7cf5-15a6-e1cc5aac505e"], "h74a0aaceg2315g4332ga4afg597868ceeb7d": ["Don't touch web, don't call web-weaver.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "8b8f9633-6b35-7cf5-15a6-e1cc5aac505e"], "hdb674e72gd27fg4079gbc46gd2bbfd1fc87a": ["Keep clear of the webs, and the spiders might not notice us.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "8b8f9633-6b35-7cf5-15a6-e1cc5aac505e"], "hd6e44ee8gd05eg46f7g9f74g369bc7d22544": ["Giant webs. They'll alert their spinners with a mere touch.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "8b8f9633-6b35-7cf5-15a6-e1cc5aac505e"], "h4dd20297g1a0ag41efg9330gbe5e67081ddc": ["Careful! 'Touch not the webs of the hairy spinner, lest you desire to become its dinner!'<i><br></i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "8b8f9633-6b35-7cf5-15a6-e1cc5aac505e"], "hc3b9ecdbgc21eg4bc9gba7cgff6287d5bd93": ["Best not touch those webs or I'll end up as a meal.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "8b8f9633-6b35-7cf5-15a6-e1cc5aac505e"], "h55ebf178gf258g4bdbga797g604addb4fea2": ["Those webs are huge. One touch, and I'm spider food.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "8b8f9633-6b35-7cf5-15a6-e1cc5aac505e"], "he2d4b475g3fc7g4686ga41dg45cf11c972ed": ["Better be careful - those webs carry vibrations.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "8b8f9633-6b35-7cf5-15a6-e1cc5aac505e"], "hf6716d00gc839g4891g8a75gf6908116716b": ["Webs everywhere. Feels like home.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "c40173f7-98c7-e141-7880-8c3aaedde327"], "hf9d08f87g0763g4c5fg8702g30a63fbd626a": ["Impressive webbing. Though I should probably worry about its creators.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "c40173f7-98c7-e141-7880-8c3aaedde327"], "h8395d96dgdcc9g4ab4gb05ag02e4e2f6fa83": ["I hate webs.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "c40173f7-98c7-e141-7880-8c3aaedde327"], "h6b8cd956g9414g47dfg9b02g6ea105d499f0": ["Oh good. Spiders.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "c40173f7-98c7-e141-7880-8c3aaedde327"], "h643db924gd4f1g4171gbaeag6c3b8a90e495": ["Webs everywhere. Which means spiders anywhere.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "c40173f7-98c7-e141-7880-8c3aaedde327"], "he6bbe94fg3e52g49efg9c93g0800429fceda": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "c40173f7-98c7-e141-7880-8c3aaedde327"], "h227f1ad3gd169g4486gb6dag00cff30e89f4": ["You could spin a cloak from all these cobwebs.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "c40173f7-98c7-e141-7880-8c3aaedde327"], "he64e2b9bg0785g4253ga6a8g3e00ff396832": ["Ick. Spider webs <i>everywhere.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "c40173f7-98c7-e141-7880-8c3aaedde327"], "h9706f9d5g3271g4eefgb73egd92aa9ab5b3f": ["These webs are everywhere.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_BottomlessWell_PAD_WebWarning.html", "c40173f7-98c7-e141-7880-8c3aaedde327"]}